lgpl3.o.ary

Class Arr<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • lgpl3.o.ary.Arr<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Ar32_2D, Ar32OfCompoBitXy, Ary2D, MapK32V, MapK32VSeq, MapK64V32, MapKSV32, PrimeAry2D

    public class Arr<T>
extends Object
implements Serializable
    The array wrapper.
    伍的特性:
    內含的項可重複.
    項有些情況下可排序.
    可同時多執行緒存取.
    存取的依據是 index.
    不可加入 null.
    當伍在膨脹中, 則執行緒安全, 且存取不易取得 null.
    Version:
    2023/11/05_12:34:56
    src
    See Also:
    Arr, Seq, Seq32, Serialized Form
